results.name: Coefficients in asymptotic expansion of sequence A259872.
link: Richard J. Martin, and Michael J. Kearney, Integral representation of certain combinatorial recurrences, Combinatorica: 35:3 (2015), 309-315.
mathematica: nmax = 25; b = CoefficientList[Assuming[Element[x, Reals], Series[x/(ExpIntegralEi[1 + 1/x]/Exp[1 + 1/x] + 1)^2, {x, 0, nmax+1}]], x]; Table[Sum[b[[k+1]]*StirlingS2[n, k-1], {k, 1, n+1}], {n, 0, nmax}]
results.author: _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Aug 05 2015
